{"id":4234,"date":"2025-06-16T16:46:45","date_gmt":"2025-06-16T09:46:45","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4234"},"modified":"2025-06-16T16:46:45","modified_gmt":"2025-06-16T09:46:45","slug":"nen-boi-kem-chong-nang-may-lan-1-ngay","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/nen-boi-kem-chong-nang-may-lan-1-ngay\/","title":{"rendered":"N\u00ean b\u00f4i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng m\u1ea5y l\u1ea7n 1 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef g\u00ecn l\u00e0n da t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng l\u00e0 l\u1edbp ch\u1eafn t\u1ed1i quan tr\u1ecdng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 <strong>n\u00ean b\u00f4i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng m\u1ea5y l\u1ea7n 1 ng\u00e0y<\/strong> \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 ngay c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"da-se-ra-sao-neu-ban-bo-qua-buoc-chong-nang-moi-ngay\"><\/span><b>Da s\u1ebd ra sao n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n b\u1ecf qua b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ecf qua kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i &#8220;t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng&#8221; l\u00e0n da m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4235\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4235\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4235\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/74-1.webp\" alt=\"Da s\u1ebd ra sao n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n b\u1ecf qua b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/74-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/74-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/74-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/74-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4235\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Da s\u1ebd ra sao n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n b\u1ecf qua b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da nhanh b\u1ecb s\u1ea1m, t\u1ed1i m\u00e0u, thi\u1ebfu s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn do b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 vi khu\u1ea9n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da b\u1ecb ch\u00e1y n\u1eafng, bong tr\u00f3c ho\u1eb7c \u0111au r\u00e1t khi ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u0103ng nguy c\u01a1 l\u00e3o h\u00f3a s\u1edbm v\u00e0 c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 ung th\u01b0 da.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, d\u00f9 \u1edf trong nh\u00e0 hay ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi, vi\u1ec7c duy tr\u00ec th\u00f3i quen d\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, \u0111\u00fang li\u1ec1u, \u0111\u00fang th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"boi-kem-chong-nang-bao-nhieu-lan-trong-ngay-la-du\"><\/span><b>B\u00f4i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng bao nhi\u00eau l\u1ea7n trong ng\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00ec t\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t b\u00f4i l\u1ea1i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n sinh ho\u1ea1t v\u00e0 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 g\u1ee3i \u00fd c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4236\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4236\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4236\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/74-2.webp\" alt=\"B\u00f4i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng bao nhi\u00eau l\u1ea7n trong ng\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/74-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/74-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/74-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/74-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4236\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">B\u00f4i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng bao nhi\u00eau l\u1ea7n trong ng\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ra n\u1eafng: B\u1ea1n n\u00ean thoa l\u1ea1i sau m\u1ed7i 2 gi\u1edd. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 l\u1edbp kem b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ea5t t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 do m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i, ma s\u00e1t ho\u1eb7c \u00e1nh n\u1eafng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u01b0\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed5 m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i nhi\u1ec1u: \u01afu ti\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng lo\u1ea1i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng th\u1ea5m n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 b\u00f4i l\u1ea1i sau m\u1ed7i 90 ph\u00fat.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi \u1edf v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng ho\u1eb7c trong nh\u00e0: D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi, tia UV v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xuy\u00ean qua c\u1eeda k\u00ednh. B\u1ea1n n\u00ean thoa l\u1ea1i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng sau m\u1ed7i 3 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 da kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e2m th\u1ea7m.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00f3m l\u1ea1i, vi\u1ec7c n\u00ean b\u00f4i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng m\u1ea5y l\u1ea7n 1 ng\u00e0y s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o th\u00f3i quen sinh ho\u1ea1t, nh\u01b0ng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1n n\u00ean duy tr\u00ec 2\u20133 l\u1ea7n\/ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"boi-bao-nhieu-kem-chong-nang-cho-moi-lan-la-du\"><\/span><b>B\u00f4i bao nhi\u00eau kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng cho m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1edbi da m\u1eb7t: Kho\u1ea3ng 2mg\/cm\u00b2 ho\u1eb7c t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi 2 \u0111\u1ed1t ng\u00f3n tay.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1edbi c\u01a1 th\u1ec3: B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n kho\u1ea3ng 25\u201330g, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi 6 mu\u1ed7ng c\u00e0 ph\u00ea nh\u1ecf.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu d\u00f9ng d\u1ea1ng x\u1ecbt: X\u1ecbt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00ean t\u1eebng v\u00f9ng, \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o l\u1edbp ph\u1ee7 m\u1ecfng 3\u20134 l\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ed5, g\u00e1y, tai, v\u00e0 m\u00e9p t\u00f3c &#8211; nh\u1eefng n\u01a1i r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb b\u1ecf s\u00f3t nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i d\u1ec5 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cac-luu-y-de-kem-chong-nang-phat-huy-toi-da-hieu-qua\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1c l\u01b0u \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ec3 vi\u1ec7c d\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da, ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00ean b\u00f4i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng m\u1ea5y l\u1ea7n 1 ng\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4237\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4237\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4237\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/74-3.webp\" alt=\"C\u00e1c l\u01b0u \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/74-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/74-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/74-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/74-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4237\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1c l\u01b0u \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thoa kem tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ra n\u1eafng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 20\u201330 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t huy c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi lo\u1ea1i da: Da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m n\u00ean \u01b0u ti\u00ean kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd, da d\u1ea7u n\u00ean d\u00f9ng lo\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a d\u1ea7u (oil-free).<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u01afu ti\u00ean s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 SPF t\u1eeb 30 \u0111\u1ebfn 50 v\u00e0 PA+++ tr\u1edf l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 kh\u1ecfi c\u1ea3 tia UVA v\u00e0 UVB.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean t\u1ea9y trang v\u00e0 r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t k\u1ef9 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf l\u1edbp kem, tr\u00e1nh g\u00e2y b\u00ed da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng gi\u00fap kem th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ec9 mua kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng t\u1eeb c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u uy t\u00edn, tr\u00e1nh h\u00e0ng gi\u1ea3 k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng ra n\u1eafng v\u00e0o gi\u1edd cao \u0111i\u1ec3m (11h\u201316h) v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam rau xanh, n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1ng cho da.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tong-ket\"><\/span><b>T\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1eb9p d\u00e0i l\u00e2u, ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecdn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng t\u1ed1t l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft n\u00ean b\u00f4i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng m\u1ea5y l\u1ea7n 1 ng\u00e0y, d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ee7 li\u1ec1u l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y. \u0110\u1eebng b\u1ecf qua b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y d\u00f9 tr\u1eddi r\u00e2m hay b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 \u1edf trong nh\u00e0.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u00e3y ch\u0103m da b\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng \u0111\u00fang t\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t &#8211; \u0111\u00fang li\u1ec1u l\u01b0\u1ee3ng &#8211; \u0111\u00fang s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho l\u00e0n da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 n\u00ean b\u00f4i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng m\u1ea5y l\u1ea7n 1 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 ngay c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4238,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4234","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4234","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4234"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4234\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4239,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4234\/revisions\/4239"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4238"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4234"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4234"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4234"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}